<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_0293723fac5d.aspx"><b>周颂·小毖</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson0293723fac5d">
<p>予其惩，而毖后患。莫予荓蜂，自求辛螫。肇允彼桃虫，拚飞维鸟。未堪家多难，予又集于蓼。</p>
